      <title>德国具有里程碑意义的支出法案面临最终障碍：值得关注的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/german-landmark-spending-bill-faces-final-hurdle-what-to-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国在债务资助的国防和基础设施支出中释放数千亿欧元的举动预计将在周五通过其最终立法障碍，当时柏林上议院的议员在柏林对措施进行投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/german-landmark-spending-bill-faces-final-hurdle-what-to-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
